<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Radioactive_contamination&action=edit&section=17.php.html" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span></h2>
<div class="reflist" style="list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
